vite:css
transforms.result: .ac,h2{text-align:center}h2{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;margin:20px 20px 40px}h2:after{clear:both;content:"";display:block}h2 .legend{display:flex;gap:15px;justify-content:end;margin-top:15px}h2 .badge{font-size:14px;font-weight:500}h2 .badge:before{border-radius:4px;content:"";display:inline-block;height:18px;margin-right:5px;vertical-align:middle;width:18px}h2 .badge.modal:before{background-color:#0070ba}h2 .badge.com:before{background-color:#def}h2 .badge.ing:before{background-color:#fff4f4}table{border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;width:100%}td,th{font-size:12px;padding:8px 10px}thead{background-color:#fcfcfc;border-bottom:1px solid #222}td,thead tr>*+*{border-left:1px solid #ddd}th{background-color:#f2f3f5}tr.row{border-top:2px solid #222}td.com{background-color:#def}td.ing{background-color:#fff4f4}td{border-bottom:1px solid #ddd}td a{display:block;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline}td a.modal{background-color:#0070ba;border:1px solid #0070ba;border-radius:4px;color:#fff;font-weight:400;padding:4px 5px;text-decoration:none}.content section+section:before{border-top:4px solid #f1f1f1;content:"";display:block;margin:30px -20px}
